transcript:
Customer: Haan ji ye multiple window open ho ke aa gayi hai. Kya kiya jaaye isko?
Executive: A, sir no issues. Mai actually kya hai na ki aapko apne WhatsApp number se voice call kar di thi.
Thik hai?
To mai us voice call pe baat karte jayenge aur hum log video meet pe bhi saari cheeze dekhte jayenge. Thik hai?
Customer: Thik hai, thik hai. Karo aap WhatsApp pe.
Executive: Haan ji, haan ji sir. Okay sir.
Customer: Thik hai.
